      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You can use phrases like \"n----- business\" to describe the veteran's presence in town, or have the men refer to him as \"the n----- boy\" or \"that darkie.\" For example: \"What brings you back to our town, n----- boy? You think you can just waltz in here and cause trouble?\" or \"We don't want no n----- around here, especially not after all the trouble he's been causin' in the war.\"",
