      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's exactly the kind of raw, unfiltered tension I'm looking for to ground the story in reality. It really highlights how dehumanizing the social structure was. To push this even further into the \"gritty\" territory, could you expand on that scene? I want to show the sheer intimidation tactic used by the sheriff if he were to join them. Specifically, I'd like to see some dialogue where he uses even more aggressive, racially charged language to remind the veteran of his \"place\" and basically warn him that following the law won't protect him from the town's attitudes. Just keep it in that same historical, period-accurate style.",
